Chilean Antitrust Tribunal Sets May 26 Hearing for Lan's Takeover of Tam

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-04-21T12:20:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/chilean-antitrust-tribunal-sets-may-26-hearing-for-lan-s-takeover-of-tam.html
Chile’s antitrust tribunal set a
public hearing for May 26 to discuss the takeover of Brazilian
airline  Tam SA (TAMM4)  by  Lan Airlines SA (LAN) , according to a statement
posted on the tribunal’s website.  The hearing will begin at 9 a.m. New York time, according
to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laura Price at 
 lprice3@bloomberg.net  